---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Salmon with Bruschetta Topping and Roasted Veggies
description: We've taken classic the Italian appetizer and made it a meal for two with succulent salmon and Parmesan-roasted potato wedges. A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set for date night!
